  "texts": [
    "The expert scores further validate the accomplishment of our goal to extract accessible and interpretable structure-property relationships in chemistry from raw data.",
    "Based on expert scores for individual studies, we noted that for case studies 1-4 XpertAI's explanations always scored better or as equally as ChatGPT, in terms of interpretability, accessibility, and usefulness.",
    "As expected, for our negative case study, experts scored XpertAI lower than ChatGPT in all categories except for specificity.",
    "We point out that, this is possibly due to inadequate training of the surrogate model used in the XAI study.",
    "We highlight that XpertAI's success is dependent upon both the XAI method and LLM's capabilities."
  ],
